      "description": "A free trial or discounted introductory period silently transitions to a paid recurring subscription. The user was not given an explicit opt-in at the moment of conversion (E1). Many jurisdictions require explicit consent at the conversion moment; federal US requirement is currently vacated (E2) but state-level requirements apply.",
